### Create Formation
POST http://localhost:2323/formations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "research-pipeline",
  "work_dir": "/tmp/research",
  "roles": [
    {
      "name": "researcher",
      "agent_id": "{{researcher_agent_id}}",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "name": "writer",
      "agent_id": "{{writer_agent_id}}",
      "count": 2
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "from": "researcher",
      "to": "writer"
    }
  ]
}

### List All Formations
GET http://localhost:2323/formations

### Get Formation by ID
GET http://localhost:2323/formations/{{formation_id}}

### Update Formation
PUT http://localhost:2323/formations/{{formation_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "research-pipeline-v2",
  "roles": [
    {
      "name": "researcher",
      "agent_id": "{{researcher_agent_id}}",
      "count": 2
    },
    {
      "name": "writer",
      "agent_id": "{{writer_agent_id}}",
      "count": 3
    }
  ]
}

### Delete Formation
DELETE http://localhost:2323/formations/{{formation_id}}

### Start Formation (Beta - returns 501)
POST http://localhost:2323/formations/{{formation_id}}/start

### Stop Formation (Beta - returns 501)
POST http://localhost:2323/formations/{{formation_id}}/stop

### Send Message to Formation (Beta - returns 501)
POST http://localhost:2323/formations/{{formation_id}}/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Research and write about AI agents"
}
